Package: backuputils
Title: Backup Utilities for AWS CLI Workflows
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Cillo", "Lab", email = "lab@example.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a small interface around the AWS CLI for copying
    local data to S3-compatible storage and verifying that uploads completed
    successfully. The package is intended as a backbone for Cillo Lab backup
    workflows and can be extended with depot-specific conventions over time.
